  ],
  "remarks": "OJSC “Biysk Production Association ‘Sibpribormash’” (OJSC BPO SIBPRIBORMASH) is a military industrial company, which ultimately belongs to the State Corporation Rostec. The company develops military equipment and weapons, including fuses for ammunitions systems and components for multiple-launch rocket systems. Therefore, OJSC BPO SIBPRIBORMASH is supporting Russia’s military and industrial complex and the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine. Furthermore, OJSC BPO SIBPRIBORMASH is supporting materially actions that undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}